results.description:
Entrepreneur Sebastiaan Tan is the Dutch version of Tim Ferriss.

In his early 20s he managed to do a full time sales job in less than 2 hours per week, while he traveled the world.

During that time he also built up his passive income to over 5k+ euro per month by investing in real estate.

He also likes to compete in extreme sports having run 10+ marathon, doing a Muay Thai Fight and being 1 of only 12 Dutch people to ever swim across the canal from the UK to France, in 15 hours.

Now he co-founded and is the CCO of a fast growing tech startup temper.works where they are revolutionising temporary hiring. With 500k investment they grew their pool of temp workers to[masked] in just 2 year.

This evening he will tell you all about how he did it.

And as a special bonus: Buying a ticket (price: €15.62) also makes you eligable to win a signed copy of Tools of Titans, written by Tim Ferriss.

https://www.eventbrite.com/e/living-the-4-hww-swimming-from-the-uk-to-france-founding-a-tech-startup-tickets-33415538776 - limited seats, first come first serve.
